txt.en: Parth Duin is located east of Crithost.\n\nYou should defeat Easterlings at this settlement.
Tolwin can be found in the hall of Crithost.\n\nYou should speak with Tolwin.
'Good work. I look up to your skills in conflict. Perhaps one day I shall be as adept as you in the ways of fighting.'

'Many Easterlings have started to gather in Parth Duin, east of here. I fear that they are grouping before marching south. Are you willing to confront them and drive them away from Talath Anor and Minas Tirith?'
Easterlings have nearly destroyed Parth Duin, a farm east of Crithost. Tolwin is determined to show the Easterlings that they are not welcome in Talath Anor and asks you to give them this message.
